  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the efficacy of dexamethasone added to ramosetron for
      preventing postoperative nausea and vomiting in highly susceptible patients following spine
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
